title: r/Choosingbeggars My Boyfriend MUST Pay Me $400,000
description:
r/Choosingbeggars The woman in today's Choosing Beggars post is out of her mind. She claims that any man who dates her has to pay all of her expenses, including a $50,000 wedding, $30,000 wedding ring, and $350,000+ in debt. Add everything up and you get well over $400,000 just for the privilege of dating her. Lady, are you out of your mind? If you like this video and want to see more, hit that subscribe button!

Watch on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JPqiSexZZvA
